Module gymmanager.gymproject3
Package gymmanager.gymproject3

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
gymmanager.gymproject3.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
Used to create new Fitness Class objects that hold the name of the class and instructor, time, list of participants, and the size of the class.
Author:
Aaron Newland, Dylan Pina
